        {
          "feedback": "Parsing is more about how those units relate to each other (the grammar), not just identifying the units themselves.",
          "isCorrect": false,
          "text": "Parsing (Structure)"
        },
        {
          "feedback": "Semantic analysis checks if the instructions make sense (e.g., is there actually a red cube?), but first, we just need to identify the words.",
          "isCorrect": false,
          "text": "Semantic analysis (Meaning)"
